query:
INSERT INTO places (atollId, name, code, type)
SELECT 
  aspo.atollId,
  aspo.name,
  LOWER(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(aspo.slug, '-', '_'), ' ', '_'), '--', '_')),
  CASE 
    WHEN aspo.spotType = 'dive_site' THEN 'dive_site'
    WHEN aspo.spotType = 'surf_spot' THEN 'surf_spot'
    WHEN aspo.spotType = 'snorkeling_spot' THEN 'snorkeling_spot'
    ELSE aspo.spotType
  END
FROM activity_spots aspo
WHERE aspo.spotType IN ('dive_site', 'surf_spot', 'snorkeling_spot')
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE type = type
